and the son of four being right in the middle and at this time this picture is across the two pages of the Jet magazine and it becomes the largest picture of a publishing jet magazine at the time and they are called by Jet magazine as quiet heroes because again they weren't involved in marching they just prefer to give up their jobs rather than tonight.

