so they would affect and be here on every level a reality that we could look forward to.

01:16:23.640 --> 01:16:39.640
because of the unevenness throughout the nation of employment and opportunities and the way that African Americans retreated in court and in legal situations.

01:16:39.640 --> 01:16:55.640
it was just something that needed to be done in this movement and a momentum that it was undergoing and a metamorphosis from just being things going on as usual.

01:16:55.640 --> 01:16:59.640
it had to change something had to be done about the conditions.

01:16:59.640 --> 01:17:15.640
again here you find a situation where the soldiers are returning from fighting America's wars, African American soldiers.

