he is at the forefront along with Matthew McCollum and others.

01:18:08.640 --> 01:18:31.640
around 1960 you also had on the college level an incident or maybe not well an incident but actually Harvey Gantt of Charleston, South Carolina was granted to the legal system and through Matthew Perry.

